":"f76277989584940c6be4eb7833df79fee8267223","tid":1787712,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T07:13:09.000Z","msg":"咁樣非禮14歲的女仔又係判1年感化<br />\n法治？<br />\n我發覺搵親學生衰11的新聞好似單單都關警甴事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇黎警甴家族真係有犯罪基因<br />\n有冇心理學家研究下香港警甴家族同平民家族的犯罪率有咩差異<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20191102/s00002/1572632473119/非禮14歲師妹-中五生判感化\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191102%2Fs00002%2F1572632473119%2F%E9%9D%9E%E7%A6%AE14%E6%AD%B2%E5%B8%AB%E5%A6%B9-%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%94%E7%94%9F%E5%88%A4%E6%84%9F%E5%8C%96&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2Bui3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=92709291\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191102%2Fs00002%2F1572632473119%2F%E9%9D%9E%E7%A6%AE14%E6%AD%B2%E5%B8%AB%E5%A6%B9-%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%94%E7%94%9F%E5%88%A4%E6%84%9F%E5%8C%96&h=190368e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20191102/s00002/1572632473119/非禮14歲師妹-中五生判感化</a><br />\n<br />\n非禮14歲師妹 中五生判感化<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】退休警察就讀中五的兒子，2016年9月開課日獲邀到中四師妹家中玩耍，其間涉大肆非禮女方。他上月經審訊後被裁定企圖強姦及非禮私處的交替控罪脫罪，但另一項非禮罪成。高院法官昨日判刑表示，案發年僅14歲女事主言行挑逗，信息內容顯示她大膽得令人咋舌，念及被告只是血氣方剛，一時衝動，判處他接受感化一年。"},{"pid":"d275de9f0e43f2864da753186cc03a0e1cfac06a","tid":1787712,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bce7763726304531dcf396087ba89370f78d4be","tid":1787712,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T07:10:22.000Z","msg":"唔洗開名？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T08:03:25.000Z","msg":"警二代咪唔洗囉"},{"pid":"9c162d91f96853d502b4ddf615ab00e315842fac","tid":1787712,"uid":72344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d275de9f0e43f2864da753186cc03a0e1cfac06a","tid":1787712,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bce7763726304531dcf396087ba89370f78d4be","tid":1787712,"uid":53062,"like":0,"disli